gemeinstrom/eegfaktura-energystore-v2
======================================

This repository is a re-implementation of the energystore component of the
eegfaktura platform. It addresses the performance and scalability limitations
of the embedded BadgerDB-backed v1 (https://github.com/gemeinstrom/eegfaktura-energystore)
by moving the time-series storage to TimescaleDB, enabling multi-replica
deployments and orders-of-magnitude reductions in per-message data movement.

The component runs alongside, not as a replacement of, v1 — clusters opt into
v2 by Helm-values selection (one variant per cluster).


